name: Arena of Ackerwalkers

abilityArray.body: Death Knights have first strike when attacking adjacent creatures.
Knights of the sun, has +1 #{aotp aotp-attack} when attacking adjacent figures.

abilityArray.title: Heal Aly
abilityArray.body: Roll one #{aotp aotp-attack}/#{aotp aotp-defense} die. Remove one damage marker from an adjacent figure if a shield was rolled. Repeat for each Knights of the Sun on the board. Use only once per turn.
Move each Blood Moon Barbarian up to 4 spaces at the end of their turn.

abilityArray.title: Trample
abilityArray.body: While attacking, if a Armored Forest Fiend would assign enough damage to destroy a defending figure, you may have it assign the rest of its damage to a figure adjacent to the defending figure.

abilityArray.title: OPPORTUNITY STAB
abilityArray.body: Deal 1 damage to one figure that was dealt combat this turn by an Armored Merfolk. Us this ability once per turn.

abilityArray.title: Back Stab
abilityArray.body: Deal 1 damage to one figure that was dealt a disengage damage by an Armored Merfolk.
